{"tid":1472229,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭不敢答的問題 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:44:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"893065870ec21d22b23e801ec9cba37983aaad6a","tid":1472229,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190814/20748304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190814%2F20748304&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXBd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=c43856be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190814%2F20748304&h=ff593c71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190814/20748304</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭不敢答的問題 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190814/large/1565687511_8aa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190814%2Flarge%2F1565687511_8aa1.jpg&h=4cc97a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n昨日林鄭月娥見記者，再次出現近期常見的哽咽，或稱「抖音」的奇特現象。犬儒者覺得她演戲，未必，所謂「林鄭抖音，未必無因」，她固然不是害怕有人將香港「推落粉身碎骨嘅深淵」，而是害怕自己被推下懸崖。恐懼肯定是真的，從她連一條普通問題也不敢答，就知道她杯弓蛇影得多厲害。<br />\n<br />\n路透社記者問：Do you have the autonomy or not to withdraw the bill？Yes or no？（你有自主權撤回法案嗎？有抑或沒有？）林鄭第一句話又是用到爛的套語：「這問題已答過幾次。」這是林鄭的口頭禪，作用是暗中貶損那條問題的價值，令人覺得是提問者沒做功課，或刻意死纏爛打。拆解方法很簡單，記者可以在林鄭回應前加一句：「我知道這問題已問過無數次，但你也迴避了無數次。是否要我向你三鞠躬，你才願意施捨一個yes或no呢？」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭講完第一句廢話後，馬上純熟地背誦兩段廢話，果然是年年考第一的背書機器。第一段廢話說中央對她和警察很有信心，第二段廢話說她已回應市民的訴求。記者不斷追問她「有沒有自主權」，她拒絕回答。不答也好，我最怕你將剛才的廢話再背一次&mdash;&mdash;那就是無差別恐襲全球觀眾的手機data了。<br />\n<br />\n其實《基本法》第四十八條已清晰界定了行政長官職權，第四項是「決定政府政策和發布行政命令」。因此，假如林鄭月娥真誠地擁護《基本法》，答案就只是天經地義的一個字：「Yes！」你拒絕回答，等於曲線告訴市民，你內心的答案是見不得光的「no」。這樣陷中央於不義，林太該當何罪？<br />\n<br />\n721警方為什麼不執法、811警方是否超執法、特首有沒有自主權講「撤回」，以上問題應該見一鑊，問一鑊。水滴石穿，這就是記者的「be water」。林鄭的招數是絕對可以破的，說穿了不過是《神鵰俠侶》中的「傻姑三招」。由於傻姑是弱智人士，太複雜的功夫學不來，於是黃藥師苦心創了三招掌法、三招叉法，特別傳授給傻姑，讓她可以三招走天涯。林鄭月娥像傻姑嗎？對不起，我侮辱了傻姑。  <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾 <br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n香港警察沒有天敵 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n政府向平民發動恐襲 (高慧然)"},{"pid":"10655239ec137a43e0b7712298103dbba717237c","tid":1472229,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46ab082fc6157659dedc9a1d2c0a66d4cab55a9","tid":1472229,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e30